CatDescriptText: Headline for image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 2, 1972, pg. 32, reads: "Scenes of Homewood Park Annual Black Arts Festival." [no cutline nor article]
TitMainTitle: Men, possibly "Afro Dogs" motorcycle club members, following Cadillac car with Claude "John" Delaney leaning out of window, in parade for Black Arts Festival, Homewood Avenue at Finance Street, Homewood
